  <entry>
    <title>使用github和hexo搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="/2021/11/15/11-15/"/>
    <url>/2021/11/15/11-15/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><h3 id="前提"><a href="#前提" class="headerlink" title="前提"></a>前提</h3><p> win 10<br> github账号<br> git环境<br> node.js</p><h2 id="步骤"><a href="#步骤" class="headerlink" title="步骤"></a>步骤</h2><h3 id="hexo-cli安装"><a href="#hexo-cli安装" class="headerlink" title="hexo-cli安装"></a>hexo-cli安装</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo-cli -g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="验证hexo-amp-npm安装"><a href="#验证hexo-amp-npm安装" class="headerlink" title="验证hexo&amp;npm安装"></a>验证hexo&amp;npm安装</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo -v<br>npm -v<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="快速生成第一篇博客"><a href="#快速生成第一篇博客" class="headerlink" title="快速生成第一篇博客"></a>快速生成第一篇博客</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo init <span class="hljs-comment">#博客初始化</span><br>hexo new blog <span class="hljs-comment">#blog是用户自定义的md文件名</span><br>hexo clean <span class="hljs-comment">#清除缓存</span><br>hexo g <span class="hljs-comment">#生成配置文件</span><br>hexo s <span class="hljs-comment">#生成本地服务器，在浏览器中输入location:4000,即可访问 </span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/blog_dir.png" alt="hexo目录下文件"></p><h2 id="未完待续"><a href="#未完待续" class="headerlink" title="未完待续"></a>未完待续</h2>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
